title: This Massive YouTube Scam Is Still Happening...
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we're taking a look at what appears to be multi-channel networks on YouTube still having a presence. These companies provide no tangible value but seem to harbor tons of channels under their wing and have near complete control of the backend. With so many channels (large and small) still under their umbrella, YouTube needs to step in and stop this from being a thing going into the future. Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
